{"tid":1757362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人關心下被捕人士？","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T13:33:24.000Z","uid":334650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8aa9247f6e3565ee8af29e2c9d06d1da904349","tid":1757362,"uid":334650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"屋企人被告暴動<br />\n全家人壓力好大，好擔心<br />\n擔心佢坐監，擔心佢未來，擔心錢<br />\n屋企人都咁折磨，當事人承受嘅壓力咪仲多<br />\n<br />\n區選完咗，個個都覺得勝利咗，<br />\n見到依家都淨係關心議員要點做<br />\n但冇人關注過啲被捕手足，<br />\n真係當咗手足係condom ?<br />\n唔好忘記，有呢個結果，都係因為呢班手足犧牲自己<br />\n<br />\n大家關心下佢地啦<br />\n612，星火真係幫唔到佢地<br />\n我哋要做嘅係爭取<strong>取消暴動定義</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爭取各位手足無罪！！！</span>"},{"pid":"d452fa243093629796d0b29fc802363803dc2d7f","tid":1757362,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8b0ed7a7f1769bc7e4301f50c96b946152ec522","tid":1757362,"uid":334650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a24099d21a11f657b2b79f3fa7b7847ecb5adf4a","tid":1757362,"uid":334650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab801337c1e05c987c7a1f6406c1336a237c53b2","tid":1757362,"uid":334650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14dfdd7de29f1b764cb35c5ff46b4bb412284c9b","tid":1757362,"uid":334650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}